Thirdly, we learn hence the duty of adding working to our wiſhing, in order to our arrival at the death of the righteous;

 and this we are to endeavour both ſeriouſly, and ſeaſonably:
               2 Pet. 1.10. 1. ſeriouſly; Give diligence to make your calling and election ſure;
               1 Cor. 15. ult. Eccleſ. 9.10. 
               Abound in the work of the Lord; Whatever thy hand findeth to do, do it with thy might: Be in good earneſt for thy precious and immortal ſoul.
